text: if anyone feels particularly iffy about the exam and doesn't want to wait 7 days between attempts (and is willing to take the exam twice) -- one suggestion I've seen online is to create throwaway account for your first attempt, then take it again if you feel confident.
tried to see if there are any terms of use that this violates, but haven't found anything yet
this will also be useful if you want to get a feel for the exam _before_ you start studying
